{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-059","title":"Sentence 59","sectionId":"sentences-051","sectionTitle":"Sentence 51-60","pageStart":386,"pageEnd":391,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":30,"duplicateEntryCount":12,"pages":[{"number":386,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 59"},{"type":"text","text":"Raised beaches often consist of areas of sand, pebbles, or dunes,"},{"type":"text","text":"sometimes containing seashells or piles of debris comprising shells and"},{"type":"text","text":"bones of marine animals used by humans."},{"type":"text","text":"上升海滩通常由沙洲、鹅卵石或沙丘组成，有时包含贝壳或者"},{"type":"text","text":"由人类用过的海洋动物的壳和骨头构成的一堆堆残渣。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句的主干是“Raised beaches often consist of areas of sand, pebbles,"},{"type":"text","text":"or dunes”。containing是现在分词，引导伴随状语，表示与谓语动词"},{"type":"text","text":"consist of同时进行。现在分词短语“comprising shells ... by humans”作后"},{"type":"text","text":"置定语，修饰piles of debris。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"beach /biːtʃ/ n. 海滩，湖滩，河滩","headword":"beach"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 coast n. 海岸"},{"type":"text","text":"shore n. 海滨"},{"type":"entry","text":"consist /kənˈsɪst/ vi. 由…组成，由…构成","headword":"consist"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 consist of 由…组成"},{"type":"text","text":"consist in 在于，存在于"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 compose vt. 构成"},{"type":"note","text":"参考 insist v. 坚持"}]},{"number":387,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"persist vi. 坚持"},{"type":"entry","text":"pebble /ˈpebl/ n. 小圆石，鹅卵石，细砾","headword":"pebble"},{"type":"entry","text":"dune /duːn/ n. 沙丘","headword":"dune"},{"type":"entry","text":"seashell /ˈsiːʃel/ n. 海贝；贝壳","headword":"seashell"},{"type":"entry","text":"pile /paɪl/ n. 堆；大量","headword":"pile"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 a pile of 一堆；很多"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 heap n. 堆"},{"type":"text","text":"stack n. 堆"},{"type":"entry","text":"comprise /kəmˈpraɪz/ vt. 包含；由…组成；由…构成","headword":"comprise"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 include vt. 包含"},{"type":"entry","text":"shell /ʃel/ n. 壳，贝壳；外壳","headword":"shell"},{"type":"note","text":"参考 shellfish n. 水生有壳动物"},{"type":"section","text":"主题归纳"}]},{"number":388,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"与“地理”相关的词："},{"type":"entry","text":"cavern /ˈkævərn/ n. （尤指大的）洞穴，山洞","headword":"cavern"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 cav（洞）+ern（表场所、地点）→大洞穴"},{"type":"entry","text":"cleft /kleft/ n. 裂缝","headword":"cleft"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 a cleft in the rock 岩石的裂缝"},{"type":"entry","text":"contour /ˈkɑːntʊr/ n. 等高线；轮廓","headword":"contour"},{"type":"entry","text":"ebb /eb/ n./vi. 衰退；退潮","headword":"ebb"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 ebb away 渐逝，衰退"}]},{"number":389,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"hemisphere /ˈhemɪsfɪr/ n. 半球","headword":"hemisphere"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 hemi（半）+spher（球）+e→半球"},{"type":"entry","text":"meridian /məˈrɪdiən/ n. 子午线，经线","headword":"meridian"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 prime meridian 本初子午线"},{"type":"entry","text":"moist /mɔɪst/ a. 潮湿的；多雨的","headword":"moist"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 damp a. 潮湿的"},{"type":"entry","text":"oasis /oʊˈeɪsɪs/ n. 绿洲；宜人之所","headword":"oasis"},{"type":"entry","text":"salinity /səˈlɪnəti/ n. 盐性，盐度","headword":"salinity"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 absolute salinity 绝对盐度"},{"type":"entry","text":"subterranean /ˌsʌbtəˈreɪniən/ a. 地面下的","headword":"subterranean"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 subterranean cave 地下洞穴"},{"type":"entry","text":"terrestrial /təˈrestriəl/ a. 陆地的；陆生的","headword":"terrestrial"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 terr（土地）＋estr＋ial（…的）→陆地的"},{"type":"text","text":"与“海洋地貌”相关的词："}]},{"number":390,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"cape /keɪp/ n. 海角，岬","headword":"cape"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 Cape of Good Hope 好望角"},{"type":"entry","text":"channel /ˈtʃænl/ n. 海峡；途径","headword":"channel"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 English Channel 英吉利海峡"},{"type":"entry","text":"coast /koʊst/ n. 海岸","headword":"coast"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 Gold Coast 黄金海岸"},{"type":"text","text":"coastal erosion 海岸侵蚀"